<plot>"Emulsion" is a dramatic neo-noir about a modern-day everyman, Dane Allen, who is forced out of his stagnant existence when he is unwittingly drawn into a vast corporate and social conspiracy. Once he realizes the severity of his situation, he must fight to regain control of a life he never fully enjoyed living. It is a story of discovery, manipulation, and the never-ending struggle between complacency and self-actualization. "Emulsion" is the first chapter of a feature length film which will follow Dane as he evolves from an utterly forgettable cog to a potent activist who brings the forces that control his life to their knees.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?176963</url></doc>
